# Knowledge Base pipeline — raw sources, OCR/extraction intermediates, and
# generated working files are large and/or copyright-sensitive and never push.
# Promotion to the committed, original-wording src/kb/rules/*.json happens only
# after human review (see docs/KB_PIPELINE.md). This is a different path and is
# NOT affected by this rule.
#
# kb/rules/*/rules.jsonl and kb/reports/conflicts.json ARE committed: they are
# the project's own encoded rule wording (not raw scans) and are the only
# inputs `npm run kg:build` needs to regenerate kb/graph/ during the Vercel
# build step — see package.json "build" script.
/kb/sources/
/kb/extracted/
/kb/processed/
/kb/cache/
/kb/embeddings/
/kb/graph/
/kb/rules/index/

